properties.name: concrete.scheduler
properties.description: 仅用于提示，实际使用为concrete.[appSet.][name.]scheduler = [aliasTo]，aliasTo说明这个名称的计划任务线程池等同于concrete.[aliasTo.]scheduler.*

properties.name: concrete.scheduler.executorSize
properties.description: 计划任务线程池的核心线程数，默认为1。键可以是concrete.[appSet.][name.]scheduler.executorSize，获取时，使用ConcreteHelper.getScheduler(String)

properties.name: concrete.service.scheduler.executorSize
properties.description: concrete服务公用的scheduler，使用ConcreteHelper.getScheduler()获取

properties.name: concrete.executor
properties.description: 仅用于提示，实际使用为concrete.[appSet.][name.]executor = [aliasTo]，aliasTo说明这个名称的线程池等同于concrete.[aliasTo].executor.*

properties.name: concrete.executor.corePoolSize
properties.description: 线程池核心线程数，默认为核心数 x 2。键可以是concrete.[appSet.][name.]executor.corePoolSize

properties.name: concrete.executor.maximumPoolSize
properties.description: 线程池的最大线程数，默认为核心数 x 4。键可以是concrete.[appSet.][name.]executor.maximumPoolSize

properties.name: concrete.executor.maxQueueSize
properties.description: 线程池最大任务数。键可以是concrete.[appSet.][name.]executor.maxQueueSize

properties.name: concrete.executor.keepAliveTime
properties.description: 线程池空闲线程回收时间，单位，秒，默认60。键可以是concrete.[appSet.][name.]executor.keepAliveTime

properties.name: concrete.service.executor.corePoolSize
properties.description: concrete服务线程池核心线程数，默认为核心数 x 2

properties.name: concrete.service.executor.maximumPoolSize
properties.description: concrete服务线程池的最大线程数，默认为核心数 x 4

properties.name: concrete.service.executor.maxQueueSize
properties.description: concrete服务线程池最大任务数

properties.name: concrete.service.executor.keepAliveTime
properties.description: concrete服务线程池空闲线程回收时间，单位，秒，默认60

properties.name: concrete.topic.executor.corePoolSize
properties.description: concrete主题发布线程池核心线程数，默认为核心数 x 2

properties.name: concrete.topic.executor.maximumPoolSize
properties.description: concrete主题发布线程池的最大线程数，默认为核心数 x 4

properties.name: concrete.topic.executor.maxQueueSize
properties.description: concrete主题发布线程池最大任务数

properties.name: concrete.topic.executor.keepAliveTime
properties.description: concrete主题发布线程池空闲线程回收时间，单位，秒，默认60

properties.name: concrete.token.maxIdleTime
properties.description: concrete令牌最大空闲时间，空闲时间大于此设置时，令牌将自动失效，单位，分钟，默认60。键可以是concrete.[appSet.]token.maxIdleTime

properties.name: concrete.client.tokenManagerKey
properties.description: 客户端令牌管理的key，键可以是concrete.client.[moduleName.]tokenManagerKey

properties.name: concrete.client.tokenTransfer
properties.description: 是否传递令牌，默认为否。当A系统的客户端运行在B系统的服务端中（B调用A），两个系统使用统一的会话管理时，应设置为true。键可以是concrete.client.[moduleName.]tokenTransfer

properties.name: concrete.client.timeout
properties.description: 请求超时时间，单位，毫秒，默认5秒。键可以是concrete.client.[moduleName.]timeout

properties.name: concrete.client.destination
properties.description: 调用服务端的目标描述符。键可以是concrete.client.[moduleName.]destination

properties.name: concrete.queue.default
properties.description: 未指定queue时默认的队列名称。键可以是concrete.[appSet.]queue.default

properties.name: concrete.signature.property.keyId
properties.description: 指定调用服务时上下文中keyId别名。键可以是concrete.[appSet.]signature.property.keyId

properties.name: concrete.signature.property.sign
properties.description: 指定调用服务时上下文中sign别名。键可以是concrete.[appSet.]signature.property.sign

properties.name: concrete.signature.property.algorithm
properties.description: 指定调用服务时上下文中algorithm别名。键可以是concrete.[appSet.]signature.property.algorithm

properties.name: concrete.signature.property.noise
properties.description: 指定调用服务时上下文中noise别名。键可以是concrete.[appSet.]signature.property.noise

properties.name: concrete.signature.algorithm
properties.description: 签名算法，默认为@Signable注解的algorithm值，否则SHA256withRSA。键可以是concrete.[paperName.]signature.[]

properties.name: concrete.client.signature.property.keyId
properties.description: 对应服务指定的keyId别名。键可以是concrete.client.[moduleName.]signature.property.keyId

properties.name: concrete.client.signature.property.sign
properties.description: 对应服务指定的sign别名。键可以是concrete.client.[moduleName.]signature.property.sign

properties.name: concrete.client.signature.property.algorithm
properties.description: 对应服务指定的algorithm别名。键可以是concrete.client.[moduleName.]signature.property.algorithm

properties.name: concrete.client.signature.property.noise
properties.description: 对应服务指定的noise别名。键可以是concrete.client.[moduleName.]signature.property.noise

properties.name: concrete.snowflake.machineId
properties.description: 雪花id生成器的配置，machineId必须是10位2机制数，前5位位数据中心号，后5位为机器号

properties.name: concrete.snowflake.dataCenterId
properties.description: 雪花id生成器的配置，数据中心号，设置了machineId则不生效

properties.name: concrete.snowflake.workerId
properties.description: 雪花id生成器的配置，机器号，设置了machineId则不生效
